### 1) Register user (optional)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Device User",
  "email": "device.user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2) Login user
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "device.user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3) Create device (replace token)
POST http://localhost:8080/devices
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Inverter Atap Timur",
  "external_id": "plant-A-01",
  "solar_profile_id": "{{solar_profile_id_optional}}"
}

### 4) List devices (replace token)
GET http://localhost:8080/devices
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 5) Rotate key (replace token and device UUID)
POST http://localhost:8080/devices/{{device_uuid}}/rotate-key
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 6) Ingest telemetry (replace X-Device-Key)
POST http://localhost:8080/ingest/telemetry
X-Device-Key: {{device_api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "device_id": "plant-A-01",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-19T08:15:00Z",
  "energy_kwh": 0.35,
  "power_w": 1850,
  "lat": -6.2,
  "lng": 106.8
}
